= Anastasiya Yushchuk

Anastasiya uYushchuk is one of the more ideologically advanced member of the SMP. As such, she can steer the main body of our association in either direction.
Julia Cwenar is a Georgian SMP revolutionary who returned from Siberian exile. She is widely viewed as the leader of the SMP. In exile, she developed a nuanced position on the war, calling for a negotiated end to the war without defeatism, although in FAIS she tends to support the Provisional Government's policies.

# actions: fundraising, organizing workers, inter-party relations, clear the agenda
# actions: relations with the NKF, support revdef, adopt revdef, support inter, adopt inter

- @improve_relations
- @support_defensism 
- @internationalism
