- @root: Return to main

@improve_relations
title: Improve our relations with the neighbours of our association.
subtitle: Yushchuk utilizes her previous position in the NKF leadership and her contacts to improve standing of our association in their eyes.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] weeks before next advisor action. ?]
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 4; m_sr_relation += 8*(1-m_dissent);

@support_defensism
title: Support Revolutionary Defensism
subtitle: Increase support for revolutionary defensism within our association.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] weeks before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 4; defensist_strength += m_support_change; defensist_dissent -= 5; internationalist_strength -= 4;

Tsereteli is advocating in favor of the Revolutionary Defensist position. 

@internationalism
title: Support Internationalism
subtitle: Increase support for internationalism among our association.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] weeks before next advisor action. ?][? if m_war_policy = 2 : We already have an internationalist war policy. ?]
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0 and m_war_policy != 2
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 4; internationalist_strength += m_support_change; internationalist_dissent -= 3; defensist_dissent += 5

We are building up support for internationalism within the association, so that we may eventually adopt this position.

@adopt_internationalism
title: Adopt Internationalism as our association policy.
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] weeks before next advisor action. ?][? if m_war_policy = 2 : We already have an internationalist war policy. ?][? if internationalist_strength < defensist_strength + social_patriot_strength: There is not enough support for this position within the association. ?]
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0 and internationalist_strength >= defensist_strength + social_patriot_strength and m_war_policy != 2
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 4; m_war_policy = 2; internationalist_strength += 5; internationalist_dissent -= 5; defensist_dissent += 15; social_patriot_dissent += 30; m_leadership = 1;

We have adopted an internationalist position, calling for an immediate end to the war.